data.description: This extensively renovated home is all set for its next long-term relationship. Swipe right on this beauty, and you'll be living the Florida dream just in time for the holidays. Every room in this house has been tastefully updated, making it feel much more spacious than its square footage suggests. You'll adore the two family rooms with chic built-in furniture and electric fireplaces, perfect for unwinding. And for the gamers in your household, this home is a winner – no more TV conflicts! The kitchen sits at the heart of the home and boasts a complete makeover. The split floor plan ensures privacy in the generously sized primary bedroom. Get ready to be wowed by the entire primary suite and its dreamy custom closet. But the fun doesn't end indoors. The backyard is fully equipped with an outdoor kitchen and a covered lounge area, ideal for relaxing while enjoying your favorite football game. There's also an outdoor shed for additional storage. When the summer heat arrives, you'll be floating in style with the expansive above-ground pool. This home checks off everything on your wish list, and it's priced affordably. Plus, it comes with recent updates, including HVAC in 2022, a hot water heater in 2022, and updated electrical panels.
